528
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:31,200
Lady Nian can only blame herself for her misfortune.

529
00:29:31,831 --> 00:29:36,881
Which girls from contributor's families were picked <br> to enter the palace?

530
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:40,000
