531
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:42,300
I have chosen,

532
00:29:42,457 --> 00:29:46,304
Censorate Censor, <br>Guwalgiya E-Min's daughter,

533
00:29:46,304 --> 00:29:51,632
as well as Guwalgiya Wen-Yuan and deputy<br>commander of the Calvalry Camp, Li Bin's sister, Li Ying.

534
00:29:51,649 --> 00:29:53,267
Please make a decision, Your Majesty.

535
00:29:53,377 --> 00:29:55,682
- Li Bin serves under Han's flag?<br>-Yes.

536
00:29:55,821 --> 00:29:58,955
Guwalgiya E-Min serves under <br>Manchu Army's yellow flag

