541
00:30:08,900 --> 00:30:13,100
I have chosen words "Qi" and "Xiang".<br>Both can be used as titles.

542
00:30:13,800 --> 00:30:16,300
Just name her Lady Qi.

543
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:18,400
Palace entrance on 1st November.

544
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:19,100
Good.

545
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:24,200
How should we dispose of Lady Zhi, <br>that was constantly with Lady Nian?

546
00:30:24,500 --> 00:30:29,600
Just let her continue to be the maid, <br>serving Lady Nian.

547
00:30:32,800 --> 00:30:37,200
Lady Cao was also very close with Lady Niang.

548
00:30:37,349 --> 00:30:38,661
Lady Cao

549
00:30:38,733 --> 00:30:44,914
Since you knew what she did, <br>why did you tell it only now?

550
00:30:44,985 --> 00:30:49,375
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.<br>I dared not to say anything.

551
00:30:49,543 --> 00:30:53,084
She was too domineering.<br>She hurt so many concubines.

552
00:30:53,253 --> 00:30:56,991
Under her power,<br> I could only remain silent.

553
00:30:57,100 --> 00:30:59,200
to protect myself and the princess

554
00:30:59,900 --> 00:31:02,000
Now that Wen-Yi grew up

555
00:31:02,100 --> 00:31:05,500
I do not want her to share my fate <br>of being compelled by other people

556
00:31:06,500 --> 00:31:12,300
It doesn't matter what happens to me.<br>But Weng-Yi is Your Majesty's daughter.

557
00:31:12,495 --> 00:31:15,611
Only after Your Majesty struck them down,

558
00:31:15,611 --> 00:31:19,799
I was able to tell everything to the Empress.

559
00:31:19,966 --> 00:31:22,905
I shouldn't have been forced by lady Niang.

560
00:31:23,101 --> 00:31:25,239
I am willing to receive any punishment.

561
00:31:25,426 --> 00:31:28,601
But I beg Your Majesty<br> not to blame for it our princess

562
00:31:28,665 --> 00:31:31,293
Your Majesty, Lady Cao was forced.

563
00:31:31,363 --> 00:31:34,264
Moreover, princess is still young.

564
00:31:34,367 --> 00:31:37,238
Sister Cao suffered greatly <br> for the sake of the princess.

565
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:40,200
Your Majesty should reward her for that.

566
00:31:51,556 --> 00:31:57,520
Lady Cao, exposing lady Niang's crimes, <br> rises your virtue.

567
00:31:58,400 --> 00:32:00,800
Thus your title rises to Pin<br> (imperial concubine),

568
00:32:01,035 --> 00:32:03,319
titled Xiang.

569
00:32:03,487 --> 00:32:07,664
Elevating ceremony on 1st November.

570
00:32:07,800 --> 00:32:11,000
Thank You, Your Majesty.

571
00:32:21,600 --> 00:32:22,700
How...?

572
00:32:25,028 --> 00:32:27,037
Was she sentenced the death penalty?

573
00:32:27,130 --> 00:32:29,592
Then relegation to Cold Palace?

574
00:32:30,500 --> 00:32:34,000
Her titles have been revoked <br> and she was demoted to Dayin.

575
00:32:34,079 --> 00:32:36,199
She is still allowed to stay in Palace of Supporting Earth.

576
00:32:36,300 --> 00:32:38,100
What?

577
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:39,900
Only this?

578
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:42,200
Emperor has known all her crimes.

579
00:32:42,793 --> 00:32:47,462
He does so due to the guilt he feels<br> when recollecting their long relationship

580
00:32:49,354 --> 00:32:51,172
What about Cao Qin Mo?

581
00:32:51,700 --> 00:32:54,100
Seven truths, three lies.

582
00:32:54,206 --> 00:32:57,066
She evaded all the bad things she has done.

583
00:32:57,173 --> 00:33:00,177
She is just a helpless mother, used by the bad consort.

584
00:33:00,300 --> 00:33:01,900
She gained sympathy and forgiveness.

585
00:33:02,431 --> 00:33:06,168
Cao Qin Mo is much more smarter than Consort Hua.

586
00:33:06,243 --> 00:33:10,518
Imperial Consort Hua, without Cao Qin Mo,
 is like an eagle with broken wings.

587
00:33:10,729 --> 00:33:13,620
Reckles, with no sense of direction,
only knowing how to snatch.

588
00:33:13,900 --> 00:33:17,200
Unable to protest when being blamed.

589
00:33:28,909 --> 00:33:32,209
Is your Majesty still worried  about Nian Gengyao's case?

590
00:33:34,900 --> 00:33:38,100
I have deprived him of all his titles,

591
00:33:38,575 --> 00:33:41,388
and made him guard of the gate.

592
00:33:41,900 --> 00:33:46,700
If he would took the punishment humbly,<br> I wouldn't have to kill him.

593
00:33:46,860 --> 00:33:48,985
But Nian Gengyao dares to wear a golden jacket

594
00:33:49,200 --> 00:33:52,100
gifted by me while on the guarding post!

595
00:33:52,800 --> 00:33:56,200
He is so blatant and caused the rumor.

596
00:33:57,700 --> 00:34:01,100
Letting everyone think I am an uncaring monarch.

597
00:34:02,208 --> 00:34:07,119
Maybe Nian Gengyao is using this jacket <br>to remind Your Majesty about his merits?

598
00:34:07,119 --> 00:34:11,405
It is only that he thinks only of himself,<br>forgetting Your Majesty's dignity.

599
00:34:11,600 --> 00:34:15,200
It should remind me of his merits?

600
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:20,100
The ministers decided that <br>he committed crime of regicide 5 times,

601
00:34:20,600 --> 00:34:23,100
crime of deceit nine times,

602
00:34:23,224 --> 00:34:29,174
crime of transgression 16,<br>crime of insolence 13.<br> In total 92 crimes

603
00:34:29,300 --> 00:34:32,000
All his crimes should bring him death penalty.

604
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:38,200
Your Majesty, <br>Lady Nian request meeting with Your Majesty.

605
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:39,800
Your Majesty.

606
00:34:40,700 --> 00:34:42,000
I refuse to see her.

607
00:34:42,100 --> 00:34:46,100
But, Your Majesty, Lady Nian kowtowed 3 times already <br>begging for an audience.

608
00:34:46,200 --> 00:34:48,700
This time even her head is bruised.

609
00:34:48,700 --> 00:34:53,900
Go and tell her, <br>that it is useless even if she kowtows 300 times!

610
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:58,200
Your Majesty. Your Majesty!

611
00:34:58,900 --> 00:35:03,400
Your Majesty. Your Majesty.

612
00:35:03,576 --> 00:35:07,937
It doesn't matter if Your Majesty punishes me

613
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:12,000
but please spare my brother's life.

614
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:15,800
Think of it like keeping a horse or a dog

615
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:19,186
to keep you company, Your Majesty.

616
00:35:19,700 --> 00:35:25,200
Your Majesty, I beg you, Your Majesty.

617
00:35:26,500 --> 00:35:32,600
Your Majesty. Your Majesty.

618
00:35:32,610 --> 00:35:36,882
Find someone to cure her wounds. <br> Let her go back to her palace.

619
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,400
Yes.

620
00:35:39,652 --> 00:35:44,228
I beg you, Your Majesty.

621
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:47,700
Your Majesty.

622
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:10,200
Because of the contribution in Qinghai, <br>I am unable to give the severest punishment.

623
00:36:10,300 --> 00:36:14,200
I am granting Nian Gengyao death by suicide, <br> Nian Fu - death by decapitation.

624
00:36:14,645 --> 00:36:18,286
His sons above 15 are to be exiled.

625
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:42,200
Things are almost done.

626
00:36:42,900 --> 00:36:49,000
I plan to promote your father<br> as Chancery board of civil,

627
00:36:49,700 --> 00:36:53,200
also for the position of <br> Left Censor in Censorate.

628
00:36:54,700 --> 00:36:56,900
Thank you, Your majesty, for Your generosity,

629
00:36:57,200 --> 00:37:02,100
but I am afraid my old father<br> will be unable to undertake such difficult tasks.

630
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:09,800
Although your father is old, <br> but having him with me brings me comfort.

631
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:13,400
Just like you do.

632
00:37:14,018 --> 00:37:18,424
Therefore the post is a reward for him,

633
00:37:19,600 --> 00:37:21,900
but also for you.

634
00:37:23,607 --> 00:37:25,742
Thank you, Your Majesty.

635
00:37:43,300 --> 00:37:45,300
Greetings, Madame.

636
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:48,300
Get up, girls.

637
00:37:48,700 --> 00:37:50,800
Lady is so kind.

638
00:37:51,050 --> 00:37:53,506
