639
00:38:03,319 --> 00:38:06,284
Its is so warm, like in springtime.

640
00:38:06,456 --> 00:38:09,755
Young Master hates the cold, so the Emperor <br> ordered to bring in bronze heaters.

641
00:38:09,794 --> 00:38:14,101
- Nice smell. What flower is it?<br>- Its Camellia Pearl. We receive all of them, except the ones for the empress.

642
00:38:14,223 --> 00:38:16,483
- Mother.<br>- Greetings, Consort Wan.

