00:38:38,110 --> 00:38:43,321
This morning she went to see the snow with girls from Officer Zhou's family and Cavalry Camp's family.

648
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:46,300
Mother, I think that

649
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:50,100
girls should not get involved in official matters.

650
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:55,000
Father was favored by the former dynasty. <br> We should remember that big tree attracts the wind.

651
00:38:55,101 --> 00:38:57,600
